,Recommended,253250,20459306,"Posted: 10 January, 2016",all,Corvos,"This. Game. Is. Amazing. However, it has pros and cons.Pros-Very promising game. This game is amazing, especially for such an early build of it.-Great concept with great features. The building is buggy, but how it works is great. The class system is nearly perfected in terms of mechanics, just needs more classes.-Extremely entertaining and very fun to play, very calm and peaceful. This game is relaxing to play, and enjoyable overall.Cons-Needs more content, this game is great as is, but I feel as though I've accomplished everything there is in the game, which didn't take long. However, this is an extremely early version of the game, so that is expected of a game in this stage.-Combat needs some working on, I've had a lot of trouble with using the party system within the game and I feel it needs some improvements.-Optimization is a major issue. Yes I know its not a priority this early in development. But it is very difficult to make villages with 20ish or more people because it gets very laggy. Optimizing the game will allow for people to make bigger and better villages which would be absolutely amazing for this game.OverallThis game is amazing, the pros may or may not outweigh the cons, thats a matter of opinion. However, I am glad i purchased this game because it is very promising, and I feel as the developers are dedicated to making this game the best it can be. You may want to wait until the game is more developed before buying, but pick it up at some point, either now, or after its more developed."
